h1.font: Step3a: Establish PK of parent entity as FK in child entity

p.font: In this case SSN is the primary key of the parent entity EMPLOYEE, so it gets mapped to a foreign key Mgr_ssn in child DEPARTMENT.

h1.font: Step3b: Map relationship attributes as attributes in child entity

p.font: Any remaining attributes on the relationship get mapped to attributes in the child entity.
p.span: In this case, Start_date on the ER diagram becomes DEPARTMENT.Mgr_start_date
